<br>
In a burst of wild red light and fire, she stood there with her wild blonde hair staring around with her wild eyes. Alecto, leader of the Furies.<br>
<br>
In a burst of wild blue light and fire, she stood there with that same grin upon her face as she looked over the Gods in her pressence. Megaera, the jealous Furie.<br>
<br>
In a burst of wild black light and fire, she stood there silent as usual holding a dead sunflower in her hand stroking the withered petals gently with a finger. Tisiphone, the Avenging Furie.<br>
<br>
<br>
Alecto grinned as she made her way towards Hypnos.<br>
&quot;Going to see Hades hmm?&quot; She snickered. &quot;Mind if we tag along, I haven't seen him in too long.&quot;<br>
<br>
Megaera strolled up towards Morphy and grinned.<br>
&quot;Nor this one sister.&quot; She grinned standing close to him. &quot;We've missed the God of Dreams, me personally.&quot;<br>
<br>
And Tisiphone sat in the corner of the room and gave a sweet smile and wave to Hypnos and the family.<br>
<br>
The Furies had Returned! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uvvvthegoddesshecatevvv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>VVV The Goddess Hecate VVV</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 93<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(12/6/01 12:11:46 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Trio of Terror</span><hr size=1> around hades and persephone sulfur seemed to engulf the air and as it fades way there stood Hecate in all her dark glory in a thin almost seethrough  slimming gown with wild serpants bounded around both her wrists and her dark hair spilling past her shoulders and down to her waist weaved in and through her hair were rare dark flowers  and on her head she wore a crown of oak leave.<br>
